      "Reduce BMNR put ladder strikes as Bitcoin reclaimed $72K above the $62.3K structural level with strong momentum",
      "Monitor oil stabilization around $94-100 range for potential bounce that could reignite inflation concerns",
      "Prepare to rotate from Maturity sector overweight if risk-on persists and growth assets continue outperforming"
    ],
    "keySignals": [
